<taxonomicName authorityName="Laurie &amp; Hill" authorityYear="1954" box="[2340,2454,987,1020]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Nyctophilus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="48" pageNumber="806" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="microdon">microdon</taxonomicName>
according to H. E. Parnaby in 2009. Monotypic.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
